sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as Admin/Volunteer
participant ProfilePage
participant AuthApiService
participant VolunteerService
participant VolunteerRepo as VolunteerRepository
participant Toast

User->>+ProfilePage: Open Profile
ProfilePage->>+AuthApiService: getProfile(studentId)
AuthApiService->>+VolunteerService: getUserProfile(studentId)
VolunteerService->>+VolunteerRepo: getVolunteerProfile(studentId)
VolunteerRepo-->>-VolunteerService: UserProfile
VolunteerService-->>-AuthApiService: UserProfile
AuthApiService-->>-ProfilePage: UserProfile
ProfilePage-->>User: Display UserProfile

User->>+ProfilePage: Choose save profile changes
ProfilePage->>+AuthApiService: updateProfile(studentId, updates)
AuthApiService->>+VolunteerService: updateUserProfile(studentId, updates)
VolunteerService->>+VolunteerRepo: updateVolunteerProfile(studentId, updates)
VolunteerRepo-->>-VolunteerService: UserProfile
VolunteerService-->>-AuthApiService: UserProfile
AuthApiService-->>-ProfilePage: updated UserProfile
ProfilePage-)Toast: addToast(success)
